  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project addresses the social, protection and educational needs of street working and displaced children in Kabul, Afghanistan and  includes a research study that will enable WCUK to improve its understanding of the prevalence and effects of child labour in the informal carpet industry in Kabul, whilst also providing basic education and psychosocial care to affected children;</narrative>
  </description>
